      </a></div></div></div><div id="cpsContentSEO"><h2 id="so-sanh-tai-nghe-airpods-4-voi-airpods-3" style="scroll-margin : 148px;"><strong>So sánh tai nghe AirPods 4 với AirPods 3</strong></h2>
