	<li><a href="https://cellphones.com.vn/sforum/cach-cai-dat-lich-am-tren-dien-thoai"><strong>Cách cài đặt lịch âm trên điện thoại Android và iPhone</strong></a></li>
	<li><strong>Các bài viết liên quan:&nbsp;<a href="https://cellphones.com.vn/sforum/tag/thu-thuat-dien-thoai" target="_blank">Thủ thuật điện thoại</a>,&nbsp;<a href="https://cellphones.com.vn/sforum/thu-thuat/ios-android" target="_blank">iOS - Android</a>,&nbsp;<a href="https://cellphones.com.vn/sforum/tag/thu-thuat-iphone" target="_blank">Thủ thuật iPhone</a>.</strong></li>
</ul></div></div></div><div class="mb-[10px] mt-[20px] w-full"><div class="flex w-full flex-wrap items-center gap-[10px] text-sm font-[500] text-textGray w600:text-base"><span class=" font-[600] ">Thẻ: </span><a class="rounded-[4px] bg-[#f5f5f5] px-[10px] py-[3px] transition-all hover:bg-cps hover:text-textWhite " href="/sforum/tag/thu-thuat">Thủ thuật</a><a class="rounded-[4px] bg-[#f5f5f5] px-[10px] py-[3px] transition-all hover:bg-cps hover:text-textWhite " href="/sforum/tag/thu-thuat-ios">Thủ thuật iOS</a><a class="rounded-[4px] bg-[#f5f5f5] px-[10px] py-[3px] transition-all hover:bg-cps hover:text-textWhite " href="/sforum/tag/thu-thuat-iphone">Thủ thuật iPhone</a><a class="rounded-[4px] bg-[#f5f5f5] px-[10px] py-[3px] transition-all hover:bg-cps hover:text-textWhite " href="/sforum/tag/apple-iphone-14">Apple iPhone 14</a><a class="rounded-[4px] bg-[#f5f5f5] px-[10px] py-[3px] transition-all hover:bg-cps hover:text-textWhite " href="/sforum/tag/wikis">WikiS</a></div></div><div class="mt-[20px]"><div class="flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-[2px]"><div class="w-full text-[#ffbf00]"><div class="flex flex-col items-end"><div class="pr-[3px]"><div class="pr-[15px]"><img alt="danh-gia-bai-viet" title="danh-gia-bai-viet" loading="lazy" width="100" height="62" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" style="color:transparent;background-size:cover;background-position:50% 50%;background-repeat:no-repeat;background-image:url(&quot;data:image/png;base64,&quot;)" src="https://cdn-static.sforum.vn/sforum/_next/static/media/danh-gia-bai-viet.98c2189c.png"></div></div><div class="py-[5px] block w1000:hidden mobile"><div class="flex"></div></div><div class="py-[5px] hidden w1000:block desktop"><div class="flex"></div></div></div></div><div class="pr-[3px] flex w-full justify-end text-base text-textGray">(0 lượt đánh giá - 0/5)</div></div></div>', '/storage/product-news/5FNHzONT5qtJaDRpY0ksX9WuZvOzwXtrQ2UwLi4J.jpg', 3, true, '2026-05-04 09:58:35', '2026-05-04 09:58:36', '2026-05-04 09:5