	<li><strong>Xem thêm các bài liên quan: <a href="https://cellphones.com.vn/sforum/thu-thuat/ios-android">iOS - Android</a></strong></li>
</ul></div></div></div><div class="mb-[10px] mt-[20px] w-full"><div class="flex w-full flex-wrap items-center gap-[10px] text-sm font-[500] text-textGray w600:text-base"><span class=" font-[600] ">Thẻ: </span><a class="rounded-[4px] bg-[#f5f5f5] px-[10px] py-[3px] transition-all hover:bg-cps hover:text-textWhite " href="/sforum/tag/apple-iphone-15-pro">Apple iPhone 15 Pro</a><a class="rounded-[4px] bg-[#f5f5f5] px-[10px] py-[3px] transition-all hover:bg-cps hover:text-textWhite " href="/sforum/tag/apple-iphone-15">Apple iPhone 15</a><a class="rounded-[4px] bg-[#f5f5f5] px-[10px] py-[3px] transition-all hover:bg-cps hover:text-textWhite " href="/sforum/tag/apple-iphone-15-pro-max">Apple iPhone 15 Pro Max</a><a class="rounded-[4px] bg-[#f5f5f5] px-[10px] py-[3px] transition-all hover:bg-cps hover:text-textWhite " href="/sforum/tag/apple-iphone-15-plus">Apple iPhone 15 Plus</a><a class="rounded-[4px] bg-[#f5f5f5] px-[10px] py-[3px] transition-all hover:bg-cps hover:text-textWhite " href="/sforum/tag/apple-iphone-15-series">Apple iPhone 15 Series</a><a class="rounded-[4px] bg-[#f5f5f5] px-[10px] py-[3px] transition-all hover:bg-cps hover:text-textWhite " href="/sforum/tag/apple-iphone-15-seires">Apple iPhone 15 Seires</a><a class="rounded-[4px] bg-[#f5f5f5] px-[10px] py-[3px] transition-all hover:bg-cps hover:text-textWhite " href="/sforum/tag/wikis">WikiS</a></div></div><div class="mt-[20px]"><div class="flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-[2px]"><div class="w-full text-[#ffbf00]"><div class="flex flex-col items-end"><div class="pr-[3px]"><div class="pr-[15px]"><img alt="danh-gia-bai-viet" title="danh-gia-bai-viet" loading="lazy" width="100" height="62" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" style="color:transparent;background-size:cover;background-position:50% 50%;background-repeat:no-repeat;background-image:url(&quot;data:image/png;base64,&quot;)" src="https://cdn-static.sforum.vn/sforum/_next/static/media/danh-gia-bai-viet.98c2189c.png"></div></div><div class="py-[5px] block